            <p rend="align(right)"><placeName>N. Y.</placeName>
                <date>March 1, 1865</date>.</p>
            <p><addressee>Reverend Isaac Leeser</addressee>,
                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>,</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">I permit myself to remind you to send 15 more<lb/> copies of the
                “Derech ha-Emunah” to <persName>S.D.Moss</persName>, <placeName>61 Catharine
                    Street</placeName>.<lb/> Please enclose the bill for the entire order, namely,
                $19.38. and<lb/> I shall send you the money as well as the balance which still
                re-<lb/>mains.</p>
            <p rend="indent(9)">Respectfully,</p>
            <p rend="indent(10)">
                <persName role="author">M. Light</persName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(11)">
                <placeName>94 East Broadway</placeName>
            </p>
